                <note rend="inline" type="source">863.00/866a: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in Austria</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Kliefoth</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1934-02-15T11:00:00-05:00"
                            >February 15, 1934—11 a.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>7. Please report more frequently during this crisis including pertinent
                    information on the welfare of Americans in Austria.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
